{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_01_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 認められたい気持ち",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Turning back the clock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースがデビューして間もない頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Shortly after Sunny Peace’s debut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（レッスン終了後。みんな寮に帰ったが、怜だけは）\n（自主練をしているというので、様子を見に来た）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Everyone has gone back to the dorms after their lessons‚ except Rei‚)\n(who’s staying behind for extra practice.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4！　1、2、3、4！\nここでジャンプ。からの、スイッチしてターン……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4! 1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4!\nJump here‚ then switch and turn…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.174166748300195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……はあ……ダメ。まだ動きが硬い\n……もう一回",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* No good. Still way too rigid…\n…One more time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.74164138827473,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3858.358611725272,
          "startTime": 29.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4！　1、2――きゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4! 1‚ 2—Eeek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜、ケガしてないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you ok‚ Rei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "え、{user}さん？\nなんでここに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? {user}-san?\nWhat are you doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、また覗きですか？\n本当に警察呼びますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Were you spying on me again?\nI’ll really call the police this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "違う違う。怜が残って練習してるって聞いたから様子を\n見に来て……それより、どこも痛めたりしてないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down. I heard you were staying behind to practice‚ so I came to check on you.\n…Anyway‚ are you ok?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "このぐらい平気です\n大げさに心配するほどじゃ……んっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine. This is nothing.\nNothing to worry about—Oww!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "無理しちゃダメだ。ちょっと待ってて\n救急箱に冷却剤とテープが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t move. I’ll be right back.\nFirst aid kit… cooling spray… athletic tape…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\nテーピングなんて出来たんですね。意外です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san.\nI’m surprised. I didn’t think you knew how to apply taping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "万が一みんなが怪我した時のために覚えたんだ\n……なあ、怜。あまり無理はしないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made it a point to learn in case someone got hurt.\n…Hey‚ Rei. Don’t push yourself too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "……別に、無理をしてるつもりはありません\nむしろ私には、まだまだ足りないぐらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m not pushing myself too hard.\nIn fact‚ I’m still not doing enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "だからこうやって残って練習しているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I stayed back for extra practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "もっともっと上手にならないと……\nきっと、認めてもらえないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to get better…\nOtherwise‚ no one will approve of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスの大会で優勝だってしてるんだ\n怜のことは今でもみんな認めてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve won a dance competition.\nEveryone approves of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "たった一回の優勝に意味なんてありません\n勝ち続けないと生き残れないんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One trophy means nothing.\nI have to keep winning to survive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "それはアイドルだって同じですよね？\nライバルに勝って、トップを目指す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the same for idols‚ isn’t it?\nYou have to beat your rivals and aim for the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "一回優勝しただけでいい気になるのは怠慢です\nそんなことじゃ、結局誰も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t rest on your laurels just because you won once.\nOtherwise‚ no one will…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……でも上ばかり見て足下がおそろかになっていたら\nまた転んで怪我しちゃうんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re looking up all the time‚ you risk losing your footing.\nYou’re setting yourself up to trip and fall again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "く……\nそ、それはそうかもしれませんけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\nM-maybe‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜の言う通り、厳しい世界なのは間違いない\n……ただ、誰も認めていないなんて思わないでほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ you’re right in thinking that this is a tough world.\nBut I don’t want you to think nobody approves of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺は怜の存在がみんなの起爆剤になると思って\n認めたから、グループに参加してもらったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I brought you into the group because I approved of you.\nI felt that you would provide a catalyst for the group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "認めて、くれたから……\n私を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You approved…\n…of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます\nでもやっぱり、どこか納得できません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nStill… that’s not enough for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "私自身がそれを、『認められている』って思えなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't feel myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（怜の実力は、メンバーにも伝わっている）\n（もう少し距離を縮めていけば、本人も気付くか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The other members all recognize Rei’s ability.)\n(If only they were a little closer‚ she’d see that…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_01-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "あの……{user}さん？\nどうしたんですか、人のことジロジロと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… {user}-san?\nWhy are you staring at me like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
